The governor lacks the power to"diminish or impair pension benefits," according to the rulingby Ingham County Circuit Court Judge Rosemarie Aquilina. vitrix new formula We travel a lot for triathlon races but rarely get to see much of the countries we visit. After the Olympics last year, the final race of the ITU World Triathlon Series was in Auckland in October so I decided to stay on in New Zealand and travel around in a camper van. New Zealand is a stunning place and it was great to go camping, hiking and rafting. We saw mountains, lakes and volcanic scenery. I remember putting my hand in a stream - the water was so hot it was smoking.
